:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$PASS:exph.
:c.Current pass number
:c.1 (always)
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$PSNO:exph.
:c.Number of formatting passes requested
:c.1 (always)
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$SYS:exph.
