:c.TWOPASS specified?
:c.0 (always)
:row refid=syssym temp.
:c.SCRIPT/VS Formatter Parameters
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$CW:exph.
:c.Control word separator
:c.Set by :xph.&period.DC:exph. (defaults to '&semi.')
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$EGML:exph.
:c.GML end-tag delimiter
:c.Set by :xph.&period.DC:exph. (defaults to '&colon.E')
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$FNAM:exph.
:c.Current input file name
