:c.GML tag delimiter
:c.Set by :xph.&period.DC:exph. (defaults to '&colon.')
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$PN:exph.
:c.Page number
:c.1 (always)
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$RB:exph.
:c.Required blank
:c.&amp.nbsp&semi.
:row.
:c.:xph.&amp.$TAB:exph.
:c.Tab character
:c.&rbl.
