:li.Document the support for :xph.&colon.LEGEND:exph.,
:xph.&colon.SAFETY:exph., :xph.SYNDEF:exph.,
:xph.&colon.SYNNT:exph. and
:xph.&colon.SYNNTREF:exph. tags which previously were either
inadvertently missing or incorrectly listed as unsupported.
:li.Restructure Appendix A.3 and A.5 to show any related &sysname.
options for each control word and tag
:li.Update the caveat section to show that &bm. :q.style:eq. files
are not processed
:li.Document the changes for R4.2
:eul.
